大约50名患者和30名医务人员确诊感染了新冠肺炎2月8日，《中国新闻周刊》独家获悉，武汉市精神卫生中心出现院内感染。
About 50 patients and 30 medical staff were diagnosed with pneumonia on February 8, China News Weekly exclusive learned that Wuhan city mental health center appeared hospital infection.
据来自该院内部的消息源透露，至少有大约50名患者和30名医务人员确诊感染了新冠肺炎。
At least 50 patients and 30 medical staff were diagnosed with pneumonia, according to sources inside the hospital.
出现聚集性发热官网显示，武汉市精神卫生中心（武汉市心理医院）是湖北省最大的一所三级甲等精神专科医院，现有六角亭、二七两个院区，编制床位950张，职工800余人。
According to the network, Wuhan Mental Health Center (Wuhan City Mental Hospital) is the largest tertiary psychiatric hospital in Hubei Province, with 950 beds and 800 employees.
武汉市民王应萍是六角亭院区老年心身病区的住院病人，她今年64岁，患有阿尔兹海默症，去年8月住进这家医院。
Wang Yingping, a 64-year-old inpatient with Alzheimer's disease, was admitted to the hospital in August last year.
1月26日，医院给王的老伴黄先生打来电话，称其妻发烧38度，于当天下午退烧。
On January 26, the hospital called Wang's wife, Mr. Huang, saying she had a fever of 38 degrees.
王应萍当天的血常规结果为白细胞正常偏低、淋巴细胞减少，与新冠肺炎早期症状相近。
The routine results of Wang Yingping's day were low leukocyte normality and lymphocyte reduction, which were similar to early CG symptoms.
27日，王应萍进行了核酸检测与CT检查。
On July 27, Wang Yingping had a nucleic acid test and CT examination.
CT显示右上肺呈片状阴影，有炎症改变，2月2日核酸检测结果为阴性。
CT revealed a patchy shadow of the upper right lung, with inflammatory changes, and negative nucleic acid test results on February 2.
据黄先生了解，此前一天，该院进行核酸检测的6人中，有4人的结果为阳性。
The previous day, four out of six people tested positive for nucleic acid at the hospital, Mr. Huang said.
2月2日与王应萍同批检测的6名病人中，有3人的结果为阳性，而这3名病人均与王应萍同一病房。
Three of the six patients tested with Wang Yingping on February 2 tested positive, all in the same ward as Wang.
2月2日，王应萍再次做了核酸检测，结果依然是阴性。
On February 2, Wang Yingping did a second nucleic acid test, the results are still negative.
但在2日晚，她的护工出现了39度多的高热。
But on the night of the 2nd, her nurses had a fever of more than 39 degrees.
护工当晚到医院发热门诊进行检测，核酸检测结果为阴性，目前在家政公司提供的住处进行自我隔离。
The nurses came to the hospital's fever clinic that evening to be tested for negative nucleic acid tests and are now self-segregated in the homes provided by the Home Affairs Corporation.
到了2月5日，王应萍再次发高烧，次日开始神志不清，双肺啰音。
On February 5, Wang Yingping had a high fever again and began to lose consciousness the next day.
黄先生称，老伴这时候白细胞已经很高了，是最高正常值的近三倍。
By this time, Mr. Huang said, the white blood cells were already very high, nearly three times the normal maximum.
王应萍的新护工也在2月5日下午出现了发热症状，并于第二天辞职。
Wang Yingping's new nurse also developed fever symptoms on the afternoon of February 5 and resigned the next day.
6日中午，王应萍被转入精神卫生中心的ICU接受治疗。
6 noon, Wang Yingping was transferred to mental health center ICU for treatment.
医院告诉黄先生，病人的血氧饱和度已经下降，可能出现最坏的结果，即病人死亡。
The hospital told Mr. Huang that the patient's oxygen saturation had decreased and that the worst possible outcome could be death.
据该院医生赵平介绍，武汉市精神卫生中心的ICU不是标准的隔离病房，也没有负压装置，只能进行气管插管、雾化等几种支持治疗。
According to Zhao Ping, the hospital doctor, Wuhan Mental Health Center ICU is not a standard isolation room, there is no negative pressure device, can only carry out trachea intubation, atomization and other support treatment.
武汉金银潭医院为该院感染新冠肺炎的精神疾病病人开设了专门病区，于2月3日启用，共有30张病床。
Wuhan Gold and Silver Pool Hospital opened a special ward for mental patients with Newly Coronary Pneumonia on February 3, with a total of 30 beds.
但赵平也表示，这个数字远远不够。
But Zhao said the figure was far from enough.
2月8日上午11时左右，金银潭医院因王应萍的核酸检测为阴性而拒绝收治。
February 8 around 11 a.m., gold and silver pool hospital because Wang Yingping nucleic acid test negative and refused to accept treatment.
目前，患者已从重症转为危重症，血氧饱和度已降到70多，并出现了因呼吸困难缺氧导致的心率加快，医院给其上了呼吸机。
At present, the patient has changed from severe to critical, blood oxygen saturation has been reduced to more than 70, and the heart rate due to hypoxia due to dyspnea has increased and the hospital has given him a ventilator.
院内感染严重，疑与调整病区有关据该院医生赵平介绍，王应萍的发热情况并非个案。
Hospital infection is serious, suspected and adjust the disease area according to the hospital doctor Zhao Ping, Wang Yingping's fever is not a case.
从1月12日开始，六角亭院区三病区（女性病区）开始出现聚集性发热现象，有10余人均出现发热症状。
From January 12 onwards, the hexagonal pavilion courtyard three disease area (female disease area) began to appear the aggregation febrile phenomenon, more than 10 people have febrile symptoms.
当时，院感科将他们界定为普通感冒，并未足够重视。
At the time, the sensory department defined them as common colds and did not attach enough importance to them.
此后出现患者高烧不退、呼吸衰竭的现象。
Since then, patients with high fever, respiratory failure.
武汉市精神卫生中心的第一例新冠确诊病例是在1月20日前后检出的，之后该病人被转到了武汉协和医院。
The first confirmed case was detected around January 20 at Wuhan Mental Health Center, after which the patient was transferred to Wuhan Concorde Hospital.
24日开始，王应萍所在的老年心身病区也出现聚集性发热现象，患者多出现高热，后经核酸检测，确诊多例新冠肺炎病例。
24, Wang Yingping's elderly psychosomatic disease area also appeared the phenomenon of heat accumulation, high fever, after nucleic acid testing, confirmed a number of cases of new crown pneumonia.
此外，该院二七院区的110病区也几乎在同一时段出现了聚集性发热情况，有20多名病人出现高热症状，此后核酸检测出至少50名阳性患者。
In addition, the 110 ward of the twenty-seventh ward of the hospital experienced a concentrated fever almost at the same time, with more than 20 patients showing symptoms of high fever, after which nucleic acid detected at least 50 positive patients.
该院另一位工作人员告诉《中国新闻周刊》，他于2月7日做了核酸检测，结果为阳性，目前症状较轻。
Another staff member told China News Weekly that he tested positive for nucleic acid on February 7 and is now showing mild symptoms.
2月8日，二七院区成瘾病区又有三名医务人员核酸检测结果为阳性，还有其他疑似患者。
On 8 February, three more medical personnel tested positive for nucleic acid in the Addicted Areas of the 27-yard district, as well as other suspected patients.
检测结果为阳性的医务人员提出，希望院方能安排统一管理，但院方的回复是，医务人员自己回家隔离，联系社区，医院目前没有统一安排。
The medical staff who tested positive submitted that they wanted the hospital to arrange for a unified management, but the hospital responded by isolating themselves and contacting the community, and there was currently no centralized arrangement in the hospital.
据赵平透露，目前武汉市精神卫生中心包括副院长以及多名科主任、护士长在内的至少30名医务人员确认感染了新冠肺炎。
Zhao Ping revealed that at least 30 medical staff, including the vice-dean of Wuhan city's mental health center, as well as directors and head nurses, were confirmed to have contracted pneumonia.
该中心一位不愿透露姓名的医生表示，他是在1月26日医院组织新冠病毒核酸检测时，检出阳性结果的。
A doctor at the center, speaking on condition of anonymity, said he tested positive for the new crown virus nucleic acid test at the hospital on January 26.
该院另一位护士表示，她是在1月31日医院组织CT筛查时发现肺部有问题，2月2日进行了病毒核酸检测，3日检测结果显示为阳性，目前症状较轻，正在居家隔离。
Another nurse at the hospital said she found lung problems during a CT scan on January 31 and a viral nucleic acid test on February 2. She tested positive three days later and now has mild symptoms and is being isolated at home.
《中国新闻周刊》联系到该中心分管副院长刘连忠，询问院内患者和医务人员感染情况。
China News Weekly contacted Liu Lianzhong, vice-president of the center, asking about the infection among hospital patients and medical staff.
刘在听完记者的问题后，马上挂断电话。
Liu hung up the phone immediately after listening to the reporter's question.
当记者再次拨打电话时，刘连忠不再接听。
When the reporter called again, Liu Lianzhong no longer answer the phone.
该院院长李毅也不愿透露具体情况，他表示，“我们现在有纪律要求，不能接受电话采访。
Li Yi, director of the hospital, also declined to give details, saying: "We are now disciplined enough not to give telephone interviews.
”对于造成院内感染和医务人员感染的原因，赵平认为有两个，一是医院重视程度不足，二是防护物资和药品未能及时到位。
Zhao Ping believes there are two reasons for hospital infections and infections among medical staff: inadequate hospital care and delays in the arrival of protective materials and drugs.
新冠肺炎疫情暴发后，1月21日，医院就宣布封闭管理。
After the outbreak of the New Crown Pneumonia outbreak, the hospital declared closed management on January 21.
但实际上，封闭措施实行得并不严格，有的家属还会往院里送东西，直到过年之后才逐渐严格起来。
In practice, however, the closure is not strictly enforced, and some families send goods to the courtyard until the New Year's Eve.
《中国新闻周刊》从医院内部了解到，1月25日左右，医院领导要求将十九病区、二病区和早期病区合并为发热隔离病区。
China News Weekly learned from within the hospital that around January 25, hospital leaders demanded that the 19, 2 and early disease areas be merged into a fever isolation area.
但合并后，新成立的病区内出现疑似病例，又随即进行病区的还原。
However, after the merger, the newly established disease areas appear suspected cases, and then proceed to the reduction of the disease area.
之后，原本未出现病例的病区也出现了疑似患者。
Since then, there have been no cases of the disease in the area also appeared suspected patients.
赵平说，医院在这个过程中考虑不成熟，没有从传染病的专业角度去进行调整，反而导致之前没有感染的病区出现了更多患者的感染，出现明显的聚集性发热的情况。
Zhao said the hospital was premature in the process and did not adjust professionally to the epidemic. Instead, it led to more infections in previously uninfected areas and a clear case of concentrated fever.
据赵平介绍，前期医务人员无防护装备，后期防护装备虽有改善，但是直到现在，进入污染区的医务人员仍然没有三级防护装备，只能做到二级防护，面罩等物资紧缺。
According to Zhao Ping, medical personnel had no protective equipment, although the late protection equipment has improved, but until now, the medical personnel entering the contaminated areas still do not have third-level protective equipment, can only achieve secondary protection, masks and other supplies in short supply.
赵平称，目前，武汉市精神卫生中心累计转到其他定点医院的病人人数已达四五十人，主要去向是金银潭医院。
At present, the number of patients transferred from Wuhan Mental Health Center to other designated hospitals has reached 40 to 50, with the main destination being Gold and Silver Pool Hospital, Zhao said.
而在2月6号，该精神卫生中心ICU已有一例确诊病人死亡，死者为老年病人。
And on February 6, the mental health center ICU has a confirmed case of death, the elderly patients.
（文中赵平为化名）值班编辑：庄梦蕾推荐阅读▼旅游业“疫”殇：春节盛宴惨淡，境内外叫“苦”一罩难求，打击“乱涨价”管用吗新冠肺炎患者粪便会传播病毒？专家：痊愈后最好再隔离两周。
Shall we fight against the spread of the virus in the feces of patients with new crown pneumonia? Expert: It's better to stay isolated for another two weeks after recovery.
